                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white mt-4">3. What data do we collect</h3>
                <p class="mt-4 text/relaxed"><strong>a.&nbsp; Personal Data provided by you through the Website</strong></p>
                <p class="mt-4 text/relaxed">While using Our Website, We may ask You to provide Us with certain Personal Data that can be used to contact or identify You. Personal Data may include, but is not limited to:</p>
