                <p class="mt-4 text/relaxed">If the Company is involved in a merger, acquisition, reorganization, assignment, transfer, change of control, or asset sale, Your Personal Data may be transferred to third parties in connection with such transaction. We will provide notice before Your Personal Data is transferred and becomes subject to a different Privacy Policy.</p>
                <p class="mt-4 text/relaxed"><strong>c. With Affiliates.</strong></p>
                <p class="mt-4 text/relaxed">We may share Your Personal Data with Our Affiliates, in which case we will require those Affiliates to honor this Privacy Policy. Affiliates include Our parent company and any other subsidiaries, joint venture partners or other companies that We control or that are under common control with Us.</p>
